Author: sodiddlydone
Text: i know what you mean a few days ago i had a binge and i ate super sweet and sugary stuff and also savory stuff after but nothing really satisfied me so i kept eating and eating until i felt like my spine was about to snap from my expanded stomach pushing against it.  at the end i was in horrible pain but still unsatisfied af

Author: saharalilyy
Text: it’s ok that u messed up, it’s happens just don’t beat yourself up about it and drink a hot drink to make u feel better xx it’s only 1 day you haven’t ruined any progress you’ve made
